        {
          "class": "DepictionMarkdownView",
          "markdown": "Meet AtlasShift \u2014 a powerful rootless location-shifting tweak that can take you from one side of the world to the other in seconds.\n\nAtlasShift gives you precise control over how apps see your location. Choose a fixed location from presets, pick a point on the map, save favorite locations, or create per-app profiles so each app can use its own custom location. For more realistic movement, AtlasShift also includes route and walking simulation with speed control and loop support.",
