        },
        {
          "class": "DepictionMarkdownView",
          "markdown": "- Per-app location profiles\n- Global fake location mode\n- Selected-app mode\n- Map-based location picker\n- Country and city presets\n- Favorite locations\n- Route and walking simulation\n- Walking speed control\n- Loop route support\n- Works with rootless jailbreaks\n- Designed for iOS 15 and iOS 16\n- Clean release build with no debug logging",
